<br>
1) Upgrade warriors (This is what people wanted. Make no mistake, NO ONE on the boards was calling for a nerf to monks)<br>
2) Nerf everyone else (in the spirit of completely tearing down and redoing game mechanics, this is the option VI opted for)<br>
<br>
Are warriors happy? Not in particular, we wanted better mitigation. However, we are finally content, to a certain extent that we have better mitigation than monks; something we were supposed to have all along. <p><center><p><font size = 3 colo = "blue"><b>Wilhelmm D'Averam<br>Warlord of the Apocalypse</b></font></p></center>

